name: Brooks Dare Underwire Bra - Women's
description: Run-ready support. Moulded cups are designed to encapsulate each breast and provide support, as well as flattering exterior lines. The high neckline and longer body provide coverage when worn alone, and adjustable straps can swap between scoopback and crossback so you can match the top you're wearing.Made of sweat wicking DriLayer® HorsePower nylon and spandex.Lightweight, moulded polyester cups for support and shape.Perforations vent excess heat.Integrated bottom band and underwire supports while you move.Minimal seams for chafe-free wear.
